title: The Bat Segundo Show -- Torrent Pack #8
description:
This is the eighth torrent pack of the literary podcast, The Bat Segundo Show, 
which can be found at http://www.edrants.com/segundo.

The podcast features indepth interviews with contemporary authors and is 
hosted by the alcoholic and blacklisted DJ, Bat Segundo.

This pack includes Shows #141-160.

141. Chimamanda Adichie
142. Brian Francis Slattery
143. Katha Pollitt
144. David Peace
145. Jeff Parker
146. Danica McKellar
147. Steven Pinker
148. Naomi Wolf
149. David Michaelis
150. James Lipton
151. Oliver Sacks
152. Richard Russo
153. Ursula Hegi
154. Tom McCarthy, Part One
155. Tom McCarthy, Part Two
156. Andrea Barrett
157. Roy Kesey
158. Yannick Murphy II
159. Garth Risk Hallberg
160. Will Self

Thanks for listening!
